### Local Testing for NFL Analyst Agent
### Run with: func start
### Base URL: http://localhost:7071

@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071

### ============================================
### CHAT ENDPOINT
### ============================================

### Chat - Ask about the Super Bowl
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "Who is playing in the Super Bowl this year?"
}

### ============================================
### SESSION RESUME EXAMPLES
### ============================================
### Step 1: Start a new session with a known ID
### Note the session_id in the response body and x-ms-session-id response header

@sessionId = to-be-filled

### Chat - Create a new session with a specific ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json
x-ms-session-id: {{sessionId}}

{
    "prompt": "What was my previous question?"
}

### Step 2: Resume the same session to continue the conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json
x-ms-session-id: {{sessionId}}

{
    "prompt": "What did we just discuss?"
}

### Step 3: Ask a follow-up in the same session
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json
x-ms-session-id: {{sessionId}}

{
    "prompt": "Based on what you told me, who do you think wins?"
}
